=== 司法任命 ===
杰克逊共任命六名最高法院大法官<ref>{{cite journal | title = Jackson's judges: Six appointments who shaped a nation | url = https://digitalcommons.unl.edu/dissertations/AAI3152613/ | last = Jacobson | first = John Gregory | journal = Etd Collection for University of Nebraska - Lincoln | date = 2004 | publisher = University of Nebraska – Lincoln | access-date = 2022-02-02 | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2021-02-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210224120936/https://digitalcommons.unl.edu/dissertations/AAI3152613/ }}</ref>，大多默默无闻。他原计划首先任命巴里，后者同意出任邮政部长后改为提名[[约翰·麦克莱恩|约翰·麦克莱恩]]<ref name="Remini-1984" />{{rp|266}}。麦克莱恩后来转投辉格党，一直是该党选派总统候选人的考虑人选。杰克逊任命的第二和第三位大法官分别是[[亨利·鲍德温|亨利·鲍德温]]与[[詹姆斯·摩尔·韦恩|詹姆斯·摩尔·韦恩]]，都在部分议题与总统意见相左，但即使杰克逊的政敌对他们也不看好。<ref name="Remini-1984" />{{rp|268}}1835年1月杰克逊提名坦尼，感谢他多年贡献，但未获参议院批准<ref name="Remini-1984" />{{rp|266}}。首席大法官马歇尔1835年去世，最高法院出现两个空缺席位，杰克逊提名坦尼继任首席大法官，[[菲利普·巴伯|菲利普·巴伯]]任大法官，经历选举换血的参议院全部确认<ref name="Remini-1984" />{{rp|266–268}}。坦尼任首席大法官直到1864年去世，最高法院在他[[坦尼法院|主持]]下维持[[马歇尔法院|马歇尔法院]]大量先例<ref>{{cite book | last = Schwartz | first = Bernard | title = A History of the Supreme Court | access-date = 2022-02-02 | url = https://archive.org/details/historyofsupreme00schw | date = 1993 | publisher = Oxford University Press | location = New York, NY | isbn = 978-0-19-509387-2 | pages = 73–74}}</ref>。他的法官生涯赢得普遍赞誉，但1857年裁决“[[斯科特诉桑福德案|斯科特诉桑福德案]]”的重大失误很大程度上抹杀大部分成就<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = The Washington Post | access-date = 2022-02-02 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201223194543/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/retropolis/wp/2017/08/16/removing-a-slavery-defenders-statue-roger-b-taney-wrote-one-of-supreme-courts-worst-rulings/ | date = 2017-08-18 | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/retropolis/wp/2017/08/16/removing-a-slavery-defenders-statue-roger-b-taney-wrote-one-of-supreme-courts-worst-rulings/ | title = Removing a slavery defender's statue: Roger B. Taney wrote one of Supreme Court's worst rulings | last = Brown | first = DeNeen L. | archive-date = 2020-12-23 }}</ref>。杰克逊卸任前一天提名[[约翰·卡特伦|约翰·卡特伦]]，后获参议院确认<ref>{{cite web | url = https://supremecourthistory.org/history-of-the-court-timeline-of-the-justices-john-catron-1837-1865/ | title = History of the Court – Timeline of the Justices – John Catron, 1837-1865 | publisher = The Supreme Court Historical Society | access-date = 2022-02-02 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210530202415/https://supremecourthistory.org/history-of-the-court-timeline-of-the-justices-john-catron-1837-1865/ | archive-date = 2021-05-30 }}</ref>。

=== 新州加入联邦 ===
杰克逊执政期间联邦新增两个州，分别是1836年6月15日加入的[[阿肯色州|阿肯色州]]<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.americaslibrary.gov/jb/reform/jb_reform_arkansas_1.html | title = Arkansas Became a State: June 15, 1836 | publisher = The Library of Congress | access-date = 2022-02-02 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220125080308/https://www.americaslibrary.gov/jb/reform/jb_reform_arkansas_1.html | archive-date = 2022-01-25 }}</ref>，1837年1月26日加入的[[密歇根州|密歇根州]]<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.americaslibrary.gov/jb/reform/jb_reform_michigan_1.html | title = Michigan Became a State: January 26, 1837 | publisher = The Library of Congress | access-date = 2022-02-02 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220123004312/https://www.americaslibrary.gov/jb/reform/jb_reform_michigan_1.html | archive-date = 2022-01-23 }}</ref>。两个州都令民主党在国会势力进一步增强，助力范布伦1836年赢得总统宝座。美国历史上新加入的州一向支持为此贡献最大的政党。<ref name="Remini-1984" />{{rp|375–376}}

== 晚年、谢世（1837至1845年） ==
